### Test Video Comments API

### 1. Get Comments for a Video
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/video-life-law/1/comments?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 2. Add a Comment
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/video-life-law/1/comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "content": "Video rất hay và hữu ích!",
  "parent_id": null
}

### 3. Add a Reply to Comment
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/video-life-law/1/comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "content": "Đồng ý với bạn!",
  "parent_id": 1
}

### 4. Like a Comment
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/video-life-law/comments/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 5. Delete a Comment
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/v1/video-life-law/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 6. Like/Dislike Video
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/video-life-law/1/like
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "action": "like"
}

### 7. Get Video with Comments
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/video-life-law/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 8. Get Popular Hashtags
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/video-life-law/hashtags/popular 